th (Cambridgeshire) Heavy Antiaircraft Regiment Royal Artillery|629th (Cambridgeshire) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment Royal Artillery]], [[Cambridge]]\n** [[646th (5th Battalion The Essex Regiment) Heavy Antiaircraft Regiment Royal Artillery|646th (The Essex Regiment) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment Royal Artillery]], [[Chelmsford]]\n\n==== 99th (Anti-Aircraft) Army Group, RA ====\n\n* '''99th (Anti-Aircraft) Army Group, RA''' , [[Southborough, Kent|Southborough]]\n** 99th (AA) Army Group Signal Squadron, [[Royal Corps of Signals]]\n** [[258th (Sussex) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Eastbourne]]\n** [[313th (Sussex) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Worthing]]\n** [[344th (Sussex Yeomanry) Light Anti-Aircraft/Searchlight Regiment, Royal Artillery|344th (Sussex Yeomanry) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Brighton]]\n** 645th (Bucks) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery, [[Aylesbury]]\n** 648th (Royal Berkshire) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery, [[Hackney, London|Hackney]]\n** [[674th (City of London Rifles) Heavy Antiaircraft Regiment Royal Artillery|674th (City of London Rifles) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment Royal Artillery]], [[Stonechat Hill]]\n\n==== 101st Coast Brigade, RA ====\n\n* '''101st Coast Brigade, RA''' , [[Dover]]\n**[[410th (Kent) Coast Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Dover]]\n** 411th (Sussex) Coast Regiment, Royal Artillery, [[Brighton]]\n** 415th (Thames and Medway) Coast Regiment, Royal Artillery, [[Gravesend]]\n** 418th (Norfolk) Coast Regiment, Royal Artillery, [[Harwich]]\n** [[419th (Suffolk) Coast Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Harwich]]\n\n=== Commander Royal Engineers, Eastern Command ===\n\n==== 25th Engineer Group, RE ====\n\n* '''25th Engineer Group, RE''' , [[Colchester]]\n** 25th Engineer Group, RE Signal Troop, [[Royal Corps of Signals]]\n** [[Kent Fortress Royal Engineers#Postwar|120th (Kent) Construction Regiment, Royal Engineers]], [[Gravesend]]\n** 122nd Field En