on]]\n** 633rd (6th Battalion, The Lancashire Fusiliers) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Rochdale]]\n** 337th (2nd West Lancashire) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Blackpool]]\n** 640th (5th (Cumberland) Battalion, The Border Regiment) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Workington]]\n\n==== 94th (Anti-Aircraft) Army Group, RA ====\n\n* '''94th (Anti-Aircraft) Army Group, RA''', [[Prestwich]]\n** 94th (AA) Army Group Signal Squadron, [[Royal Corps of Signals]], [[Prestwich]]\n** 890th Anti-Aircraft Fire Command Battery, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Prestwich]]\n** 310th (Manchester) Light Anti-aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Manchester]]\n** 644th (The South Lancashire Regiment) Light Anti-Aircraft/Searchlight Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Warrington]]\n** 349th Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Hoylake]]\n** 634th (The Lancashire Fusiliers) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Salford]]\n** 652nd (Manchester) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Wigan]]\n\n==== 95th (Anti-Aircraft) Army Group, RA ====\n\n* '''95th (Anti-Aircraft) Army Group, RA''', [[Newport, Wales|Newport]]\n** 95th (AA) Army Group Signal Squadron, [[Royal Corps of Signals]], [[Newport, Wales|Newport]]\n** 891st Anti-Aircraft Fire Command Battery, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Newport, Wales|Newport]]\n** [[390th (King's Own) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Liverpool]]\n** 635th (Royal Welch) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Caernarfon|Carnarvon]]\n** 636th (Royal Welch) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Newtown, Wales|Newtown]]\n** 637th (3rd Battalion, The Monmouthshire Regiment) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Abergavenny]]\n** 666th Light Anti-Aircraft/Searchlight Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Brierley Hill]]\n** 672nd (Worcestershire) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], Langley\n\n==== 96t