ex) (Mixed) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]]\n**[[565th (Surrey) Searchlight Regiment, Royal Artillery]]\n\n=== 2nd Anti-Aircraft Group ===\n\n* '''2nd Anti-Aircraft Group''', [[Aldershot]]: covering [[Wales]], and [[South West England]], coinciding with Southern Command and Wales part of Western Command.\n* 12th Anti-Aircraft (Mixed) Signal Regiment, [[Royal Corps of Signals]], [[Bristol]]\n* 2nd Anti-Aircraft Group (East) Transport Column, [[Royal Army Service Corps]], [[Reading, Berkshire|Reading]]\n*2nd Anti-Aircraft Group (West) Transport Column, [[Royal Army Service Corps]], [[Bristol]]\n*2nd Anti-Aircraft Ordnance Company, [[Royal Army Ordnance Corps]]\n*7th Anti-Aircraft Workshop Battalion, [[Royal Electrical and Mechanical Engineers]]\n*'''61st (Hampshire) Anti-Aircraft Brigade''', [[Fareham]]\n**61st Fire Control Troop, [[Royal Artillery]]\n**524th (Bournemouth) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Bournemouth]]\n**535th (Hampshire) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Eastleigh]]\n**[[393rd (Hampshire) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery|393rd (Hampshire) (Mixed) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Southampton]]\n*'''71st (Welsh) Anti-Aircraft Brigade''', [[Cardiff]]\n**71st Fire Control Troop, [[Royal Artillery]]\n**520th (Glamorgan) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Cardiff]]\n**534th (Mixed) Light Anti-Aircraft Regiment, [[Royal Artillery]], [[Swansea]]\n**[[282nd (Welsh) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Cardiff]]\n**[[602nd (Welch) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery|602nd (Welch) (Mixed) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Cardiff]]\n**[[603rd (1st Battalion, The Monmouthshire Regiment) (Mixed) Heavy Anti-Aircraft Regiment, Royal Artillery]], [[Newport, Wales|Newport]]\n*'''72nd (Gloucestershire) Anti-Aircraft Brigade''', [[Bristol]]\n**72nd Fire Control Troop, [[Royal Artillery]]\n**523rd Light Anti-Aircraft Regimen